cogimag.java.keyboard.development

Class SampleExtendedKeyMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • cogimag.java.keyboard.KeyMap
      • cogimag.java.keyboard.development.SampleExtendedKeyMap

  • public class SampleExtendedKeyMap
extends KeyMap
    Demonstration of extending the built-in KeyMap with a map for a different keyboard. The parent's static method runs first. The child's static method overwrites (does not append) the values put by the parent. The HashMap of this class will have the key-value pairs generated by the developer's keyboard by running MapGenerator.
